        <h2>About Virat Kohli</h2>
        <p>Virat Kohli is an Indian international cricketer and former captain of the Indian national team. He is one of the greatest batsmen in the history of cricket and has inspired millions with his passion, discipline, and consistency on the field.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">Read More</a>
